task.summary: Corrects the puzzle piece placing bug, and document the environment class
A working implementation. Not done convergence test.
Added a graded intensity difference based reward
Adds discretization in gradients to make the state space finite
Adds checker for image being color or grayscale
restructure CNN model, to reduce the weights to be learnt for the 2x2 dummy grid
Reduces disc io by removing jigsaw piece saving and fetching. All done in memory
Adds visualization library for nearest neighbours
